## Resolved Questions

- ✅ **App Identity** — Icon concept generated (minimal flat play-triangle inside an "O" circle, red on dark). Accent color: `#E50914`.
- ✅ **Branding Direction** — Netflix-style, clean and premium. No cosmic/space theme.
- ✅ **Download Tool** — **yt-dlp + ffmpeg** directly (no vid-dl-cli-only). User is familiar with yt-dlp. This also means users don't need a separate custom binary — just `yt-dlp` and `ffmpeg` on PATH.

