## IPC / Backend Architecture

The main process modules from Streambert will be **ported with improvements**:

### [REUSE] AllManga Pipeline
Port the entire [allmanga.js](file:///d:/Projects/Orion%20-%20A%20Multiverse%20of%20Stories/streambert-main/src/ipc/allmanga.js) — hex cipher, AES-256-CTR decryption, GraphQL queries, local proxy server. This is battle-tested and mirrors ani-cli's approach.

### [REUSE] Ad-Blocking & Session Setup
Port the blocked hosts list and session interceptor from [index.js](file:///d:/Projects/Orion%20-%20A%20Multiverse%20of%20Stories/streambert-main/index.js). Same header stripping, same m3u8/vtt interception.

### [REUSE] Download Pipeline
Reuse Streambert's download queue, progress parsing, subtitle bundling, and file management concepts, but Orion's backend should spawn direct `yt-dlp + ffmpeg` tools from PATH or Orion's app-managed tools folder. Do not require the `vid-dl-cli-only` helper folder.

### [REUSE] Subtitle System
Port [subtitles.js](file:///d:/Projects/Orion%20-%20A%20Multiverse%20of%20Stories/streambert-main/src/ipc/subtitles.js) — SubDL + Wyzie search, ZIP extraction, subtitle file management.

### [REUSE] Player Controls & Window Management
Port [player.js](file:///d:/Projects/Orion%20-%20A%20Multiverse%20of%20Stories/streambert-main/src/ipc/player.js) — mpv/VLC launch, video progress query across frames, window controls.

### [REUSE] Secure Storage
Port [storage.js IPC](file:///d:/Projects/Orion%20-%20A%20Multiverse%20of%20Stories/streambert-main/src/ipc/storage.js) — safeStorage for API keys.

### [REUSE] Utils
Port the renderer-side utilities — TMDB/AniList API layer, player sources, caching, age ratings, AniSkip, etc.

