## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `npm run build` — Vite production build completes without errors
- `npm start` — App launches, loads the setup screen

### Manual
- First-launch flow: enter TMDB key → validates → shows home page
- Home page: hero banner rotates, carousels scroll, cards show posters
- Search: `Ctrl+F` → type "Inception" → results appear → click → movie page
- Play: click Play on a movie → webview loads Videasy → video plays
- Source switch: change to VidSrc → player reloads with new source
- Anime: search "Attack on Titan" → detected as anime → AllManga source → video plays
- Downloads: capture m3u8 → open download modal → start download → progress shows
- Library: save to watchlist → appears in library → remove from watchlist
- Settings: change accent color → UI updates immediately
